# Mattermud - Mattermost Multi-User Dungeon

## Summary
Mattermud is a mud for mattermost. Any user in the instance can create a player and play in this RPG game. A bot will serve as Game Master, telling the player what they see and what happens in the world. The extension of the game is quite simple, by adding new JSON files with new areas, items or monsters.

## Link
* https://github.com/larkox/mattermost-plugin-mattermud
